@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 120
skinparam ranksep 60
skinparam padding 15
skinparam defaultFontSize 13

actor "Admin/Developer" as AAdmin

rectangle "Traffic Camera Browser" {
  boundary "Admin Management UI" as UI
  control "Camera Management Controller" as CMC
  entity "Admin" as AdminEntity
  entity "Camera" as CameraEntity
}

AAdmin --> UI : add/remove camera
UI --> CMC : management request
CMC --> AdminEntity : verify admin login/role
CMC --> CameraEntity : add/remove camera record
CMC --> UI : show success/error

note bottom of UI
After logging in, administrators can manage
the cameras displayed on the platform.
end note
@enduml